<bioghist encodinganalog="545"><p>Resident of <geogname normal="Port Huron (Mich.)">Port Huron, Mich.</geogname>, served as corporal and sergeant, 
<corpname normal="United States. Army. Infantry, 339th. Company B.">Co. B, 339th Infantry</corpname>.</p></bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520"><p>
<genreform normal="Letters (correspondence)">Letters</genreform> describing daily activities; also 
<genreform normal="Diaries.">diaries</genreform> containing brief descriptions of his activities in Russia and of his passage home. 
Most of the collection has not been digitized.
</p></scopecontent>

